ected as the host for the sub regional workshop. The Permanent Secretary also highlighted that this was a workshop with a difference, as the meeting clearly focused on the countries\u2019 specific needs and priorities, and the support required by countries to address these. The partnership among UN Agencies who operated as One UN was also commended. Workshop participants from Fiji doing a group exercise 26.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "45d3c025-61ea-4e6e-9ff3-acea27dfc0e7": {"__data__": {"id_": "45d3c025-61ea-4e6e-9ff3-acea27dfc0e7", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/sub-regional-workshop-mdg-based-planning-costing-and-budgeting-western-pacific-countries", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Sub Regional Workshop on MDG-based Planning, Costing and Budgeting for Western Pacific Countries", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/sub-regional-workshop-mdg-based-planning-costing-and-budgeting-western-pacific-countries", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "7a86f6ce6813d88f77e43e2b2cf420e553319f900135f5c3b52c1aeae8946f11"}, "2": {"node_id": "9da7231b-7389-4c1b-9a15-2c8306f697b0", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/sub-regional-workshop-mdg-based-planning-costing-and-budgeting-western-pacific-countries", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "9e2884988cc51f5404f7c8dfbb50a86d5932bf1e